title: I Won't Marry The Enemy Prince
alternative_title: I Won't Marry The Villanous Prince ; 我才不嫁反派皇子
status: I Won't Marry The Villanous Prince ; 我才不嫁反派皇子
genres: 三福动漫 San Fu Dong Man
description:
Description :
        The “God of Annihilation”, Yan Xi, defeated the enemy country but brought back one of the country’s princesses. The doll-like 5-year-old Tao Xiaowei disturbs all the chickens and dogs in the palace, while the cold-blooded prince gets his first experience at raising a child. A few years after defeating the enemy country and returning home, the pair sets off destroying other adversaries and slashing love rivals, with the two only holding each other in their eyes.
